    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Forward Hub and Ring Gear Assembly</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To assemble, reverse the disassembly procedure.</para>
            <randlist type="bullet">
                <item>
                    <para>Lightly lubricate the thrust washer with clean transmission fluid to hold it in place during
                        assembly.
                    </para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>When installed, make sure the retaining ring is fully seated in the forward ring gear ring
                        groove. The tips must face downward against the hub.
                    </para>
                </item>
            </randlist>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
